text:
I am having the same issue reported here and was hoping that someone can assist...
<https://community.HubSpot.com/t5/APIs-Integrations/Create-Line-Item-error-Property-values-were-not-valid/td-p/361981>

The customer has hundreds of products that were created by the Ecommerce Bridge and are in use on existing deals etc.  We must continue to use these products.
Everything works fine with products that were inserted by means other than the Ecommerce Bridge.

When adding line items to deals and using an Ecommerce inserted product id using a V1 or V3 API call:

<https://api.hubapi.com/crm/v3/objects/line_items>
{
"properties": {
"hs_product_id": 16438860,
"name": "CX22 Ceiling Antenna",
"quantity": 2,
"price": 449
}



The api gives this error and none of these validated fields were sent:
{
    "validationResults": [
        {
            "isValid": false,
            "message": "\"ip__ecomm_bridge__ecomm_synced\" is a read only property; its value cannot be set.",
            "error": "READ_ONLY_VALUE",
            "name": "ip__ecomm_bridge__ecomm_synced"
        },
        {
            "isValid": false,
            "message": "\"ip__ecomm_bridge__source_app_id\" is a read only property; its value cannot be set.",
            "error": "READ_ONLY_VALUE",
            "name": "ip__ecomm_bridge__source_app_id"
        },
        {
            "isValid": false,
            "message": "\"ip__ecomm_bridge__source_store_id\" is a read only property; its value cannot be set.",
            "error": "READ_ONLY_VALUE",
            "name": "ip__ecomm_bridge__source_store_id"
        }
    ],
    "status": "error",
    "message": "Property values were not valid",
    "correlationId": "XXXXXXXX"
}
